ScenarioHeader.Title: FDR_Using _Custom_SQL_Applied _Transformations

ScenarioDataSource.SQL_Text:
SELECT
    c_customer_sk,
    c_customer_id,
    c_current_cdemo_sk,
    c_current_hdemo_sk,
    c_current_addr_sk,
    c_first_shipto_date_sk,
    c_first_sales_date_sk,
    c_salutation,
    c_preferred_cust_flag,
    c_birth_day,
    c_birth_month,
    c_birth_year,
    c_birth_country,
    c_login,
    c_email_address,
    c_last_review_date,
    c_full_name,
    c_created_date,
    CASE WHEN (CHARINDEX(' ', c_full_name) = 0) THEN '' ELSE SUBSTRING(c_full_name, 1, CHARINDEX(' ', c_full_name) - 1) END AS c_first_name,
    SUBSTRING(c_full_name, CHARINDEX(' ', c_full_name) + 1, LEN(c_full_name)) as c_last_name,
    FORMAT(CONVERT(DATE, c_created_date),'yyyy-MMM-dd') as Format_Date
FROM Temp.dbo.customer;

SELECT
    c_customer_sk,
    c_customer_id,
    c_current_cdemo_sk,
    c_current_hdemo_sk,
    c_current_addr_sk,
    c_first_shipto_date_sk,
    c_first_sales_date_sk,
    c_salutation,
    c_first_name,
    c_last_name,
    c_preferred_cust_flag,
    c_birth_day,
    c_birth_month,
    c_birth_year,
    c_birth_country,
    c_login,
    c_email_address,
    c_last_review_date,
    c_created_date,
    FORMAT(CONVERT(DATETIME, c_created_date, 120),'yyyy-MMM-dd') AS Formatted_Created_Date
FROM Temp.dbo.customer_dim;
